b'Our teachers are His Majesty\xe2\x80\x99s soldiers, and they are here today, arming themselves with the knowledge and determination to bring up generations who are confident and capable of conquering the challenges of their time'

b'No one is more worthy of educating future generations than those who travel distances before sunrise to attend classes, and to learn how to encourage inquisitiveness. This is ambition, the foundation of citizenship, and the values Your Majesty seeks in builders of the future'

b'I know you never wait for a word of thanks. Even so, from myself and on behalf of every student, father, mother, teacher, and principal \xe2\x80\x93 thank you, @KingAbdullahII. If not for your vast heart \xe2\x80\x93 where every child can find a home \xe2\x80\x93 this academy would not have seen the light'

b'The lucky ones among us find someone to inspire them and push them toward their goal. I am fortunate to have found that in the person closest to me, His Majesty @KingAbdullahII, and I am honored to be his lifelong companion'

b'There is no one more worthy of our resources, time, and effort than the person standing at the front of the classroom \xe2\x80\x93 the teacher who spends a third of her day with our children, and who imparts principles and values to them alongside math and language skills'
